tent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qyy1665702732474.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qyy1665702732474.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qyy1665702732474.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qyy1665702732474\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      enhanced numbers\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use an enhanced Oracle number mapping.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qyy1665702732474__topic_d55667e1_d55668e1_d55669e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qyy1665702732474__p_d55670e1_d55671e1_d55672e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ORA_PARAMS = enhanced numbers</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qyy1665702732474__p_d55673e1_d55674e1_d55675e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ORA_PARAMS = en</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qyy1665702732474__section_tn4_qm4_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d737301e66\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qyy1665702732474__p_d55679e1_d55680e1_d55681e1\">By setting this option, NUMBERS that are defined with\n            scaling will have one more digit of precision, thus making them equal to NUMBERS without\n            scaling.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531483\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531483\" data-toggle=\"modal